  "texts": [
    "Our approach addresses the challenges of extracting and organizing domainspecific knowledge from unstructured scientific literature.",
    "By grounding the KG construction process in a taxonomy (NASA's GCMD), we ensured semantic consistency and reduced hallucinations commonly associated with LLMs.",
    "Our experiments demonstrated the effectiveness of integrating RAG with LLMs for KG construction, particularly in improving precision and reducing false positives in entity recognition and relationship extraction.",
    "The use of few-shot learning further enhanced the model's ability to adapt to the climate science domain, even with minimal training examples.",
    "Additionally, our curated dataset and annotation pipeline provide a valuable resource for future research in climate science information extraction."
  ],
